# Frontend Deployment Rules

This repo is **frontend only**. Backend code belongs in `horizon-lens-backend`.

## Cloudflare Workers

- App is served at `https://isaiash.com/horizon/` via the standalone `horizon-lens` Worker.
- Push to `main` deploys via `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` (requires `CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN`, `CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID`).
- Vite `base` must stay `/horizon/`.
- Static assets must use `import.meta.env.BASE_URL`, never hardcoded `/assets/` or `/chile-dem.png`.
- Do **not** use Cloudflare Pages for this repo.
- Do **not** deploy through `digital-garden-isaias`; this repo owns `/horizon` on `isaiash.com`.

## API configuration

- Backend URL is set at build time via `VITE_API_BASE`.
- Value is the host only (e.g. `https://horizon.ac3eplatforms.com`), **without** `/api` suffix.
- All fetch calls go through `frontend/src/api/client.ts`.

## Do not add

- Backend, DEM data, Docker Compose, or database schemas to this repo.
